{"tid":1317232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7月14號沙田總結新聞：大量恐佈分子襲擊遊行市民","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T18:08:35.000Z","uid":216555,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9583d8bdaaa6741ee5645d040ed8345717c7d289","tid":1317232,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:53:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今天大量恐佈分子襲擊遊行市民</span></span><br />\n疑似大批恐佈分子冒充警務人員手持武器初步估計是和IS恐怖分子有關<br />\n亦有有市民被恐怖分子包圍，期間亦有<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恐怖分子將市民眼珠刮下以往IS 亦有使用匕首將整個頭顱割下</span></span><br />\n圖片如下（網上圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y6AEhXC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy6AEhXC.png&h=6bf7eee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n和平遊行竟然受到恐怖襲擊有市民感到憤怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2a0tbh6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2a0tbh6.png&h=9a27857a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/scnfAKM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FscnfAKM.png&h=eb3159dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5owoKC7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5owoKC7.png&h=b3660a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 市民遇上自稱警務人員應如何自保和查證對方身份?<br />\n警務人員在以下情況須出示警察委任證：<br />\n便衣警員：執行職務或在行使警察權力時，必須表明身份及出示委任證。<br />\n軍裝警員：一般無須主動出示警察委任證，但如市民提出要求，他們亦須出示委任證，除非情況不容許，或要求不合理。<br />\n當警員出示委任證，只須向提出要求的市民展示委任證，而不可將委任證轉交任何市民查閱。 如市民對警務人員身份或委任證存有懷疑，可立即聯絡就近警署查詢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nzJiyxy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnzJiyxy.png&h=ec3bcec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香島日報</span></span>"},{"pid":"d75f50ad4cf3e33f9ae1e86229a53c428570970a","tid":1317232,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好驚啊一定要推"},{"pid":"4e8dcd37e282305189d6b5a543724a267e056fe8","tid":1317232,"uid":58453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:59:00.000Z","msg":"推呀 出街要小心"},{"pid":"04be202094d7f1d1b802d0bf10ef56b56de49885","tid":1317232,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:59:42.000Z","msg":"我都巧驚驚 香港安全就要靠阿蛇la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ccc22a6e96f85d3913fd7c80975399b204b4b1","tid":1317232,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eSo6Hxv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeSo6Hxv.png&h=a22dca95&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}